I always try to make it a point to be in-tune with nature by indulging in the current season. Interacting with snow now, crunching leaves in autumn, walking naked and tanning whole day in summer. The way you think also changes, for most it's unconscious, but you can also feel it.

Each season comes with its blessings and vices. In spring people tend to be more horny, it is mating season. In summer I am at my absolute laziest, I turn into liquid, but I am also manic. Learning how the season affects you and others is good knowledge, needs to be "felt" though
